% To save the workspace to a MAT file named filename.mat
save filename

%save the workspace variable to a file named datafile.mat
save datafile.mat

%To clear the workspace for creating new program
clear  % clears the workspace

%load the variables from the mat file
load filename

%load the variables from the file datafile.mat
load datafile.mat

%The variable data is listed in the workspace.You can see contents of any variable by entering name of the variable
myvar

%display the contents of the variable data
data  % displays all the variables in the data

To clean the workspace, use clear command
clc  %cleans up the command window


